FBIS4-15018 "drsov066_b_94019" FBIS-SOV-94-066 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Approves Parliament Development Body Yeltsin Approves Parliament Development Body LD0504180194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1600 GMT 5 Apr 94 LD0504180194 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] The Russian president signed an instruction today aimed at improving the provision of information and experts' services for the Federal Assembly and facilitating interaction between the bodies of state power. The document approves the setting up of the foundation for development of parliamentarism in Russia. The government is instructed to register the foundation. It is recommended that the Moscow government should allocate 1,000 square meters for this foundation's offices.
